8d9f			 
8d9f			toUpper: 
8d9f			;A is the char. 
8d9f			;If A is a lowercase letter, this sets it to the matching uppercase 
8d9f			;18cc or 30cc or 41cc 
8d9f			;avg: 26.75cc 
8d9f fe 61		  cp 'a' 
8da1 d8			  ret c 
8da2 fe 7b		  cp 'z'+1 
8da4 d0			  ret nc 
8da5 d6 20		  sub 'a'-'A' 
8da7 c9			  ret 
